  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Tracing Readiness",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Service Graph Request Rate",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (client, server) (rate(traces_service_graph_request_total[5m])) OR vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "{{client}} → {{server}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Trace-derived Error Calls",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 1
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m])) OR vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "error calls",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Trace-derived Latency P95",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket[5m])) by (le)) OR vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "p95 latency",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Logs Carrying trace_id",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 9
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{stack=\"$stack\"} |= \"trace\" or {stack=\"$stack\"} |= \"trace_id\"",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "dedupStrategy": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Tempo / TraceQL Hints",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 17
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Explore → Tempo\n```traceql\n{ status = error }\n```\n\n```traceql\n{ duration > 500ms }\n```\n\n```traceql\n{ resource.service.name = \"oauth2-proxy\" }\n```\n\n```traceql\n{ resource.service.name = \"keycloak\" }\n```\n\n### Readiness\nThis dashboard is useful as soon as:\n- OTLP spans reach Tempo\n- service graph metrics are generated\n- logs start carrying `trace_id`\n"
      }
    }
  ],
